    <title>RackNerd促销vps升级教程</title>
    <link href="https://blog.redsnailmc.com/posts/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <id>https://blog.redsnailmc.com/posts/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</id>
    <published>2025-07-30T00:42:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-07-30T02:58:20.248Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>这家服务商总会出一些便宜的vps，眼馋买了一个1c1g版本的，但后来1g内存不太够用了，于是就想升级到2gb内存版本，vps面板上是没有升级选项的，不知道是不是因为促销vps的问题，但经过测试这样的vps是可以发工单升级的。</p><h3 id="升级教程"><a href="#升级教程" class="headerlink" title="升级教程"></a>升级教程</h3><p>首先去发个工单，类型选择销售，告诉他你需要升级服务器，就像下面这样:</p><p><img src="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/1.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="1"><br>（由于这里我已经升级过了，所以产品 id 上面写的是2gb KVM）</p><p>等几分钟就会有人回你了:</p><p><img src="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/2.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/2.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="2"><br>这里要求截图你想升级的vps计划，截图后上传到工单附件里就行了。</p><p>再等待一会，工作人员就会回复可以升级，并询问是否确认，回复确认即可。<br><img src="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/3.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/3.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="3"><br><img src="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/4.png" class="lazyload" data-srcset="https://r2.redsnailmc.com/RackNerd%E4%BF%83%E9%94%80vps%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/4.png" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///////yH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" alt="4"></p><p>确认后就会给你开一个账单，支付账单后你需要回复他们，告诉他们你已经支付了账单，然后就可以升级成功了。</p><h3 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h3><p>1.升级之后磁盘分区需要手动调整（嫌麻烦的可以直接重装系统）<br>2.他们告知你升级完成后，你需要去他们的管理面板重启vps才可以使升级生效（用ssh等方式重启vps系统不行）<br><br>至此vps 就已经升级完成了</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
